This paper focuses on generating review texts from images, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also mentions making adjustments to the existing model, which involves machine learning and optimization, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely sub-category as well. The paper also mentions the importance of subjective information and emotional guidance, which may involve sentiment analysis and affective computing, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) possible sub-categories.
